title: Pela adds a few new designs to Pixel 6, Pixel 6 Pro collections
content:
Last month we took a look at the eco-friendly and bizarrely comfortable Pela case line for the Pixel 6 Pro, and in the time since, the case maker has expanded its lineup with a few new cases for both of Google’s latest phones.
